\newlabel{fig:patent-diagnosis}{{2}{7}{Patent temporal/provenance diagnosis in terms of mean \AUPRC {} under the expanded panel. Left: pooled year-band slices, with 2021 merged into the recent stratum. Right: test-set overlap buckets computed from the saved overlap score. Error bars denote seed std over the matched 3-seed runs. In the expanded panel, \texttt {RF} dominates the aggregate temporal benchmark, while \texttt {DTI-LM} remains strongest only in the lowest-overlap bucket.\relax }{figure.caption.9}{}}
