\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {A6}{\ignorespaces Targeted robustness probes added after the external review. The non-patent temporal probe tests whether the promoted patent ranking persists when patent provenance is removed. The scaffold probe tests whether the synthetic \texttt  {unseen\_drug} ordering survives a stricter chemistry-aware holdout. The controlled patent variants reduce recurrent pair and seen-drug overlap to test how much the patent ordering depends on allowable overlap. Values are mean $\pm $ std over three seeds.\relax }}{13}{table.caption.16}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tab:robustness-probes}{{A6}{13}{Targeted robustness probes added after the external review. The non-patent temporal probe tests whether the promoted patent ranking persists when patent provenance is removed. The scaffold probe tests whether the synthetic \texttt {unseen\_drug} ordering survives a stricter chemistry-aware holdout. The controlled patent variants reduce recurrent pair and seen-drug overlap to test how much the patent ordering depends on allowable overlap. Values are mean $\pm $ std over three seeds.\relax }{table.caption.16}{}}
